[data: {"text": "- Nypro is one of the world's leading makers of precision custom injection", "faviconURL": "https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/1x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png"} data: {"text": " molded plastic parts. \n\n\n- Their president, Gordon Lankton, meets with a technician in the prototype room to see a new NovaPlast molding machine in", "faviconURL": "https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/1x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png"} data: {"text": " action. \n\n\n- The NovaPlast had revolutionary mold changing capabilities, which could represent Nypro's future. \n\n\n- Lankton is pondering how to integrate the NovaPlast machines into Nypro's 21 manufacturing plants around the world. \n\n\n- Key to Nypro's success was", "faviconURL": "https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/1x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png"} data: {"text": " Lankton's view that maintaining a vigorous growth rate was not just the result of a successfully executed strategy, it was a key input in the formula for success.\n\n\n- Nypro had a competitive internal rivalry among their various plants. \n\n\n- The plants were located near their customers and were identical, each with identical equipment. \n\n\n- Nypro developed a decentralized location strategy, with each plant operating as its own company, separate from other facilities. \n\n\n- Innovation is a result of competition and was encouraged at Nypro, as long as the innovations were disseminated throughout the company. \n\n\n- Nypro used Continuous Improvement (CIT", "faviconURL": "https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/1x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png"} data: {"text": ") teams to work with customers on solving production and profitability problems. \n\n\n- Nypro's decentralized sales group approved every new customer and every major new customer program in the company. \n\n\n- Three options had begun to emerge for the rollout of the NovaPlast machines:\n - Build a new plant dedicated to NovaPlast machines.\n - Install two or three machines in each of Nypro's plants.\n - Focus on making NovaPlast successful at a single plant.", "faviconURL": "https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/1x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png"}]